title: Why cant i transfer To EUW From OCE?? HELP!

replies.body:
Hey Dude,

In order to transfer your account you'll need to [contact support](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new). Please see [this post](https://boards.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/announcements/f6bvYNQx-important-notice-transfers-disabled-from-sep-14th-to-nov-21st) for details.

Due to a number of issues around the world over the last week, our ticket queues are overloaded and it may take a couple of days for them to complete this request.
They have disabled transferring for some reason until november
